---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Service">
  <section style="padding: 5rem 2rem; background: white; min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);">
    <div style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 900; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0 0 3rem;">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">By using WoWo SIM services, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">2. Service Description</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">WoWo SIM provides data-only eSIM services. Plans do not include voice calls or SMS. Coverage is subject to local network availability.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">3. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">A full refund is available if the eSIM has not been activated and the request is made within 15 days of purchase. Services already utilized where data has been consumed are not eligible for refunds.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">WoWo SIM is not liable for interruptions in service due to factors outside our control including local network outages, device incompatibility, or force majeure events.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #162544; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">5. Contact</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@wowosim.com" style="color: #03def3;">support@wowosim.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
